y Says. 9 00 Bill WeUa\nWeather 9:30 Woman\u2019s\n8:45 Bill WeUa World\n7.00 Munyan, 9:55 health Chat\nNews 10:00 News.\n7:15 Bill WeUa Band*\u2019and*\n7.45 The Rambler.\nWQAM Radio\nMONDAY EVENING\n8.00 lop 40 Show 9:55 News\n6:55 News I 10:00 Courtney\n7:00 Jerry Wichner 10:55 News\n7:55 News I 11:00 Courtney\ngOO Jerry Wichner 11:55 News\n8:53 News j 12:00 Courtney\n9:00 Jerry Wichner 12:55 News\nJ. 30 Rhythm At\nRandom\nTCESDAY MORNING\n1.00 Mus;e I hru 8 55 News\nThe Night 9:00 Gerry Spinn\n5:55 News 9:55 News\n6:00 560 10:00 Gerry Spins\n6:35 News 10:55 News\n7:00 Breakfast 11:00 Chuck\nClub Dougherty\n7 55 News 11:55 News\n8 nd Chuek\nDougherty\npep club held a prayer meeting\nto pray for Abbington's recovery.\n\"At one time at least 250 people\n\u2014whites. Negroes and Indians\u2014\nwere l?ned up to assist Abe in any\nway they could.\u201d football coach\nMax McKenzie, said\n\"I believe he's over the hump\nnow.\u201d\nLarry Raker. Indianapolis wai\nterweight boxer, won 35 of 45 ama\nteur bouts before turnins to the\nprofessional ranks in 1\u00b052.\nTUESDAY AFTERNOON\n12 0O News 2 30 Your Vet diet\n12:15 Korla Pandit 3:00 R Milland\n12:30 World Turns* 3:30 F.dge Xignt*\n1:00 Playhouse 4:00 Headlines\n1:30 Housepartv* 430 Pope\u00bbe Pise\n2 00 Big Payoff* 5:45 News*\n'Denotes Network\nOLD ISLAND\nTRADING POST\n\u201cTha Internstior al Shop\"\n301 WHITEHEAD STREET\nGIFTS ANTIQUES\nTUESDAY MORNING\n7:00 Today* 9 30 Treas. Runt*\n7:25 Fishing 10:00 Price, Right*\n7:30 Todav io 3O Truth. Cons\n8:25 Fla. Report 11 00 Tic Tsc Dgh\n8:30 Today* U;3O Could B* You*\n9:00 A. Francis*\nTUESDAY AFTERNOON\n12:00 Tex. Jinx* 3:45 Rcmances*\n12:30 Hulicks 4 00 Heroes, Wert\n1:00 Club 60 5:00 F ather\n1:30 Bride. Groom* I 5:30 Patti Pag*\n8:00 Matinee* I 5 45 News*\n3:00 Queen*\nFORMICA\nand Plastic\nWALL TILE\nHEADQUARTERS\nKey West\nFloor Covering\n132 DUVAL STREET\nPHONE CY 6-2512\nTUES\u00bbAY AFIERNOON\n12:00 Mom* 3:45 Romances*\ni 1:30 Bride. Groom* 4:00 Comedy*\n2 00 Matinee* 4:30 Ramar\n3:00 Queen* I 5:00 Movie 7\n\u2018Denotes NetworT\nDrink...\n11 \u2014\u2014\u2014a\u2014\nKey West 1600\nIVESDAY AFTERNOON\n12.00 Harvev* 3 30 News*\n12:15 Brownlie 3 35 Melodies*\n12:30 Weather 4:00 Mus. Corner\n12:35 News 5.00 Melodies*\n12:45 Music 5:30 News*\n12:55 Warm I p* 5:35 Melodies*\n1:00 Game of Day* 5:45 Sports\n\u2022Denotes Network\n_______________\nWKWF\n1600\nON YOUR DIAL\nMiami 610\nTL'ESDAY AFTERNOON\n12:00 News 3:00 Five Star\n12:15 Luncheon Matinee*\nMusic 3:30 Hilltop\n12:45 Weather House*\n12:50 Top Tune 3:45 Pepper\n12:55 Tell Me, Young\u2019s Family*\nDoctor 4 no News*\n1 oo News* 4 ns Traffic Tufiss\n1:05 Bill Goodwin* 5.45 News\n2:00 News*\n2:05 True Con\nfessions*\n2:30 Woman In\nMy House*\n2:45 Dr. Gentry*\nFor Quality\nPrinting\nThe Artman Press\nCITIZEN BLDG. CY 6-5661\nMiami 560\n1 TLLBDAY AFTERNOON\n12.00 Chuck 2:55 News\nDougherty 3.00 Gerry Spinn\n12:55 News 3:55 News\nI 1:00 Gerry Sptnn 4:00 Top 40 Show\ni 1:55 News 4:3S News\n1 2:00 Gerry Spinn 5:00 Top 40 Shew\n5:55 Sports\nI I\nTHIS SPACE\nFOR SALE\nCall CY 6-5661\n1,","height":"26523","width":"19815"}}
